  <md:title>Overview of Metabolic Reactions </md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Describe the process by which polymers are broken down into monomers</item>
<item>Describe the process by which monomers are combined into polymers</item>
<item>Discuss the role of ATP in metabolism</item>
<item>Explain oxidation-reduction reactions</item>
<item>Describe the hormones that regulate anabolic and catabolic reactions</item>
</list></md:abstract>
